","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2685632513","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685632513","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTYzMjUxMw==","status":"current","title":"Tpago","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10589376},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685632513","tinyui":"/x/AYATo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685632513","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685632513/Tpago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685632513"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"02b1c62d-f280-467d-a4c8-3a57e2af09b8\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para la vista de <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PRYLDP/pages/281706497/Definiciones+-+N+mero+de+referencia+e+Hist+rico+de+pago#Hist%C3%B3rico-de-Pagos\">Hist&oacute;rico de Pagos</a>, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"5f0f0f5470b8a90025b61555\" ri:local-id=\"39351a81-2342-443b-95f4-691e64bf7e5c\" /></ac:link> .</p><p>Las horas estimadas son: <strong>85</strong></p><p>Fecha de Inicio: <time datetime=\"2025-05-19\" /> </p><p>Fecha estimada de Entrega: <time datetime=\"2025-06-06\" /> &rarr; Considerando que <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"5f0f0f5470b8a90025b61555\" ri:local-id=\"7ae2a050-aa30-4eb6-9ee5-950e079e5127\" /></ac:link> esta 6hs por d&iacute;a</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 444.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 124.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 191.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Crear dataset que liste los pagos de un suscriptor en su suscripci&oacute;n</p><ul><li><p>Deber&aacute; traer tambi&eacute;n datos del suscriptor como RUC, EMAIL, TEL&Eacute;FONO y si est&aacute; activo.</p></li></ul></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear endpoint que consuma el nuevo dataset y represente los pagos</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear maquetado de vista de pagos de un suscriptor</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">15</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-portal</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Modificar la vista de Suscripciones para poder acceder desde ah&iacute; a la vista de Hist&oacute;rico de Pagos</p><ul><li><p>El nombre del suscriptor se ver&aacute; como un link que al hacer hover cambiar&aacute; el mouse a una mano y se podr&aacute; seleccionar para acceder ala vista.</p></li></ul></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-portal</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear opci&oacute;n para volver a listado de Suscripciones desde la vista de Hist&oacute;rico de Pagos</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-portal</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear endpoint para poder consumir el listado de Pagos de un Suscriptor desde la API</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">10</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">external-commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Consumir el endpoint nuevo para traer todos los pagos del suscriptor y representarlos en la tabla</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">payment-link-portal</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Salida a Staging</p><ul><li><p>Integraci&oacute;n de los flujos</p></li><li><p>Creaci&oacute;n y correci&oacute;n de PRs</p></li><li><p>Pruebas locales</p></li><li><p>Armado de ramas</p></li><li><p>Deploy a STG</p></li><li><p>Pruebas iniciales en STG</p></li></ul></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">75</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">10</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>85</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3971350529"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":91992785},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3971350529/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3971350529/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3971350529/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3971350529/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3971350529","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3971350529/Hist+rico+de+Pagos+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3971350529","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3971350529","tinyui":"/x/AQC27","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}